attributes.text: Go west on NF-11 toward NF-720
At the stop sign, turn right on US-20 (Santiam Hwy)
At the traffic light, turn left on W Airport Rd
Continue forward on Denny School Rd
At the stop sign, turn left on OR-34 (Corvallis-Lebanon Hwy)
Turn left on Corvallis-Newport Hwy (OR-34-BYP) toward Philomath / Junction City / Oregon Coast
At the traffic light, turn right on SW 15th St
At the traffic light, turn left on SW Washington Way
Turn left on SW Jefferson Way
Make a U-turn and go back on SW Jefferson Way
Turn right on SW Campus Way
Finish at Location 2, on the left
